data.description: Welcome to the perfect blend of elegance and comfort in this captivating residence located in a quiet community in Waldorf!  Boasting a wealth of features and recent updates, this home is sure to fulfill your every need.  The allure begins as you step inside to discover the thoughtfully designed layout spanning three levels.  The main level seamlessly blends together a traditional floor plan with a formal living room and open floor with a great room.  The open kitchen, dining and family room is perfect for entertaining, family gatherings or quiet evenings.  Just imagine hosting, cooking while your family and friends gather round.  Kitchen boasts a new microwave, all new backsplash and beautifully refaced cabinets.  Main floor is complete with a convenient half bathroom.  Head upstairs to discover four spacious bedrooms, each providing its own unique charm.  The primary bedroom boasts a gorgeous full bath and a generously sized walk-in closet, offering both style and functionality.  The hallway full bath rounds out the upper level.  Descend to the finished walkout basement and you will find a versatile space offering endless possibilities. Whether you envision it as a playroom, additional family/rec room, craft space, or even a home office, this area adds valuable square footage to accommodate your lifestyle.  The convenience of a full bathroom in the basement ensures comfort for all.  Step outside to discover the jewel of this property—a serene koi pond and luscious landscaped backyard.  The water feature adds tranquility to your outdoor space along with the new tiled patio. Fall in love with the beautifully landscaped front and back yard with roses, Japanese maple and palms.  The spacious yard, combined with the quiet community setting, provides an ideal backdrop for outdoor activities and relaxation. Last but not least, the home boasts a 2-car garage and a spacious 4-car driveway. Peace of mind with the several home updates including a new roof installed in 2023 and a sump pump installed in 2019 - with a battery backup. Rear fence was installed in 2023 as well.  Main and lower level flooring is by Empire Flooring with transferable warranty.  Inquire for more details on 2.625% assumable VA loan. Embrace the opportunity to make this residence your own, where the perfect combination of indoor and outdoor living creates a harmonious living atmosphere. Four lakes inside the neighborhood with walking trails make for a great way to get outside. Perfectly located with easy access to 301 and surrounding amenities including St Charles Towne Center and Waldorf Marketplace. This home has it all - schedule your private showing today!  Home qualifies for the MCCT loan program. Buyer may be able to purchase with 0% down payment and a $5,000 lender grant.
